@Comment:	Time is 0:38
@Comment:	Chi follows words with finger; reading seems to require a lot of effort to Chi but she was not exclusively a slave of the print: she comments on the faces on the moon and sun , and says she's hungry too; Mot helps to sound out words , suggests how to break up words like started; the most interesting thing about this reading is certainly that it still contains talk about the story
